    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      
    <a href="/guides/first-time-home-buyer/" class="block p-6 bg-[var(--bg-surface)] border border-[var(--border-default)] rounded-2xl hover:border-[var(--color-usa-blue)] transition-all shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">First-Time Home Buyer Guide 2025</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)]">Buying your first home is an exciting milestone, but the process can often feel overwhelming. From saving for a down pay...</p>
